entities.name: English Bulldog
entities.description: A charming and quirky breed of dog. Requires specific care and attention, including frequent baths and daily cleaning of wrinkles.

entities.name: Bathing
entities.description: Frequent baths are necessary for English Bulldogs to maintain their health and hygiene.

entities.name: Wrinkle Cleaning
entities.description: English Bulldogs have wrinkles that need to be cleaned every day or every other day to prevent infections and maintain their health.

entities.name: Stubbornness
entities.description: English Bulldogs can be very stubborn, which can affect their training and behavior, such as housebreaking.
